36#include <stdio.h>
37#include <string.h> /* for strlen */
38#include "gmp.h"
39#include "gmp-impl.h"
40
41void
42mpf_dump (mpf_srcptr u)
43{
44 mp_exp_t exp;
45 char *str;
46
47 str = mpf_get_str (0, &exp, 10, 0, u);
48 if (str[0] == '-')
49 printf ("-0.%se%ld\n", str + 1, exp);
50 else
51 printf ("0.%se%ld\n", str, exp);
52 (*__gmp_free_func) (str, strlen (str) + 1);
53}
